you have to create a bot:
login to telegram web and search for bot father
press start and follow the further instruction, it will give you a token at the end
run the telegram_info.py script and it will give you various information about your bot
you can find your chat id there in the "chat" key
now get your bot token and chat id and store it in a .env file and load it before running further code

source:
https://gist.github.com/nafiesl/4ad622f344cd1dc3bb1ecbe468ff9f8a
